translated: Zachrisson, Axel Vilhelm, municipal district doctor, Gothenburg, born on November 17th, 1884 in Gothenburg to Bernhard Z. and Johanna Nilsson. Married on the 14th with gymnastics director Margaretha Loberg. Children: Bo, born in 1915, medical licentiate, assistant doctor at Örnsköldsviks hospital, Arne, born in 1919, medical candidate, Gothenburg. Completed high school in Gothenburg in 1904, gymnastics director in 1908, medical candidate in 1912, and medical licentiate in 1917 in Stockholm. Acting assistant doctor at Stockholm's general relief institution hospital from 1915 to 1916, attending physician at Kroppefjäll sanatorium in 1916, acting assistant doctor at Sahlgr. Hospital, medical department in 1917, intern there from 1917 to 1918, second physician from 1919 to 1920, assistant physician at Gibraltar healthcare facility from 1920 to 1924, telegraph physician in Gothenburg since 1920, municipal district doctor since 1924.
